      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PLUTOCRACY (5) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 22.42 beating Lilly's Wish. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. PAW WHISPER (1) was quickly into stride and found the front last start to record an all-the-way win (22.44) at this track in a Bottom Up - Restricted Win over 390m. The form out of her last race has been franked. One of the prime contenders. SAINT XAVIER (4) finds it hard to win. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing third (22.74) at this track. Solid record here at the distance winning eight races. Expecting another good run. LEKTRA HOPPER (7) was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back.",
